Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.93,0:38:56.94,Default,SHINCIHI,0,0,0,,حقّاً؟
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.94,0:38:58.20,Default,NAKAMICHI,0,0,0,,.بجِدّ
